;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502017101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502017101.json-->
::'''Cong:''' Like willow leaves moving at a speed of knots, super duper love you lots.
::'''Cong:''' Autumn winds and moon rises on buildings glow, love can also move as slow.
::'''Cong:''' ...Writing poetry is so easy. Why doesn't she like me? What am I missing?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I wouldn't like you either.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017105-->
:::'''Cong:''' It's pure emotion. Can't you hear that? I feel like I'm on equal grounds with the seven sacred poets of Xianzhou.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This poem of yours is terrible...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017107-->
:::'''Cong:''' You don't like it...? Look, "knots" and "lots"... it all rhymes... four lines of heptameter.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502017108-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017108-->
::'''Cong:''' ...Ah, forget about it. I'm not arguing with you. To be honest, I don't even really get what's so good about poetry, and can't really tell what's good poetry.
::'''Cong:''' You, however, seem to have unique insights into poetry. Tell me, other people pour out their love and emotion, and I'm here writing out my true feelings too. What am I doing wrong?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's missing the sense of culture and taste...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017111-->
:::'''Cong:''' Culture? Taste? What's that? Don't just invent new words to trick me.
:::'''Cong:''' ...Maybe you aren't tricking me. *sigh* You're right. I'm lacking in culture and taste.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I actually think you write with your own style!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017114-->
:::'''Cong:''' My own style... Thank you. Even though I can't really tell if this is meant as a compliment or consolation.
:::'''Cong:''' But in the end, even if you do like it, she doesn't like it. So it's useless...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502017116-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017116-->
::'''Cong:''' *sigh* ...Anyways, do you need anything?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502017101_30-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502017101_30-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502017104: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502017104.json-->
::'''Cong:''' You're a sorrowful sigh at the end of the world, while I am just an insignificant screw. I'm at a loss, helpless in ways to mend your broken heart. Oh, Jingzhai...
::'''Cong:''' Oh, you're here. What brings you here?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
