:{{DIcon|Talk}} The Ambrosial Arbor is growing again...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502017201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G52/Act502017201.json-->
::'''Cong:''' I composed a poem for this. Listen up. I'll chant it for you...
::'''Cong:''' Ahem... Scalegorge waters surge and flow; mighty tree you grow and grow; a sip for you, a sip for me; growing like a kebab tree.
::'''Cong:''' Huh? Do you like it? ...Uh, I can tell by your expression that you're not a fan... Forget it, I'll come up with another.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
