:{{DIcon}} I want to chat with you...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502017105: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502017105.json-->
::'''Cong:''' Alright. It's not like I have any inspiration... What are you after? Is it about artifex technology?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502017402-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017402-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You know about artifex technology?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017403-->
:::'''Cong:''' Yeah, I'm an artisan at the Artisanship Commission, and I'm kind of a big deal. My boss loves me and he said, "Cong, if you just work on your EQ a little, you'll be a Master Artisan in another hundred years."
:::'''Cong:''' Frankly speaking, I think he's right, as I really don't have a high EQ... But, I've heard them say that I've gotten better lately. If it's not sarcasm, it probably means I have improved.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you still write poems now?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017406-->
:::'''Cong:''' I do, but I no longer rely on the Poetic Genius Ingenia. I prefer to write the poems myself.
:::'''Cong:''' It turns out that writing poems isn't as serious a business as I used to think... I've fallen in love with it.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What about those Poetic Genius Ingenia?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017409-->
:::'''Cong:''' I talked to them about their thoughts and left them to pursue what they desired.
:::'''Cong:''' The Gloomy Poet is a quirky one. It told me that the right amount of melancholy makes it feel safe, so it asked me to adjust its settings. You can still bump into it if you're lucky.
:::'''Cong:''' What exactly is melancholy then, you might ask? When you're experiencing the emotion, you'll be in agony. When you aren't, you'll miss it.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What about Jingzhai...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502017413-->
:::'''Cong:''' I know what she thinks, and I will leave her alone.
:::'''Cong:''' However, it'll take a long time before I can convince myself to give up on her. Anyone who's been through this would understand.
:::'''Cong:''' Don't worry. I won't neglect my job at the Artisanship Commission.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I have nothing else to ask.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: All_Talk_End-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502017105-->
